						<summary>

						

						<p>On the beam of the verandah of the Śiva temple east of the village.</p>						

						<p>The record is in archaic characters assignable to about the 8th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift of 20 <hi rend="italic">maṟuttu</hi> by three persons (names not clear) to Paṟarēva-svāmin.</p>						

						</summary>
